deck_description:
One of the coolest fusion deck of yugioh.

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

(Yeah, <span class="Y2IQFc" lang="en">probably a pure branded despia deck would be stronger, but there is more variety in this deck and it's more fun to play.)</span>

Live Twin Engine with enough hand-traps to survive most boards.

There are two Extra Deck Packages you can run depending on what you're playing against;

I normally play the Link disciple, Link devotee, I:P Masq. package with an Accesscode as a win-con but this XYZ package is also great. Up to your preference.

&nbsp;

<strong>Watch the Video for fun! </strong>

Ojama King will show you the way. teach your opponent the way by slamming some fat meat on his side of the field so he can't set any cards. I hope you enjoy the games and if you have extra resources give it a try.

&nbsp;

Disclaimer: This deck will make you want to put your hand through the monitor if you're playing in Plat, the games recorded were in Plat but my god dealing with 15 + Handtraps every game just makes you cynical at some point.

Cubic otk

Or Link/XYZ plays to beat your opponent

&nbsp;
